<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 26 Apr 2024 06:16:33 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>中国干邑白兰地销量推动人头马君度第四季度销量创佳绩</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/remy-cointreau-reports-better-than-expected-q4-sales-2024-04-26/</link><description>人头马君度周五公布第四季度销售额降幅远小于预期，称中国的“显着增长”帮助推动其干邑部门的业绩远高于分析师的预期。</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Apr 2024 05:33:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/remy-cointreau-reports-better-than-expected-q4-sales-2024-04-26/</guid></item><item><title>北京车展：主题与亮点</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/beijing-auto-show-themes-highlights-2024-04-26/</link><description>中国最大的车展在北京开幕，各大品牌展示了他们最新的电动汽车（EV），突显出全球最大的汽车市场已经处于全电动状态，并且不会回头。</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Apr 2024 05:07:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/beijing-auto-show-themes-highlights-2024-04-26/</guid></item><item><title>香港3月房价上涨1.1% 近一年来首次上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/hong-kong-march-home-prices-up-11-first-rise-nearly-year-2024-04-26/</link><description>在金融城市取消限制以提振疲弱的房地产市场后，香港私人住宅价格在3月份扭转了连续10个月的下跌趋势，较2月份上涨1.1%。</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Apr 2024 03:51:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/hong-kong-march-home-prices-up-11-first-rise-nearly-year-2024-04-26/</guid></item><item><title>博世将在中国城市推出城市自动驾驶导航功能</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/bosch-launch-urban-navigate-on-autopilot-functions-chinese-cities-2024-04-26/</link><description>博世移动部门董事长马库斯·海恩 (Markus Heyn) 周五表示，博世 (ROBSCJ.UL) 将于 5 月份通过其先进的驾驶辅助系统推出城市自动驾驶导航 (NOA) 功能。</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Apr 2024 03:18:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/bosch-launch-urban-navigate-on-autopilot-functions-chinese-cities-2024-04-26/</guid></item><item><title>随着与贸易伙伴的紧张局势加剧，中国通过关税法</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-passes-tariff-law-tensions-with-trading-partners-simmer-2024-04-26/</link><description>中国周五通过了一项法律，这使得其最大的贸易伙伴毫无疑问可以反击，如果他们对世界第二大经济体的出口征收关税，华盛顿和布鲁塞尔就工业产能过剩问题将矛头指向北京。</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Apr 2024 02:14:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-passes-tariff-law-tensions-with-trading-partners-simmer-2024-04-26/</guid></item><item><title>北京市将补贴国产人工智能芯片 目标到2027年实现自力更生</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/beijing-city-subsidise-domestic-ai-chips-targets-self-reliance-by-2027-2024-04-26/</link><description>随着中国寻求发展半导体产业并减少对外国技术的依赖，北京市当局宣布对购买国产人工智能（AI）芯片的企业提供补贴。</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Apr 2024 01:58:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/beijing-city-subsidise-domestic-ai-chips-targets-self-reliance-by-2027-2024-04-26/</guid></item><item><title>日本央行维持利率不变，亚洲股市上涨，日元跌至 34 年来新低</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-04-26/</link><description>日本央行（BOJ）在为期两天的政策会议结束后维持宽松货币政策立场，周五交易波动较大，而亚洲股市在大盘中上涨。</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Apr 2024 01:49:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-04-26/</guid></item><item><title>外交部长王告诉布林肯，美中关系中“负面”因素正在形成</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/blinken-meet-chinese-counterpart-wang-yi-beijing-2024-04-26/</link><description>外交部长王毅周五在与美国外长安东尼·布林肯会谈时表示，美国正在打压中国的发展。布林肯正在北京访问，旨在解决超级大国之间的贸易和政策分歧。</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Apr 2024 00:39:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/blinken-meet-chinese-counterpart-wang-yi-beijing-2024-04-26/</guid></item><item><title>日本央行维持利率不变，日元跌至34年新低</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/yen-its-weakest-decades-boj-meets-2024-04-26/</link><description>日本央行周五维持利率不变后，日元兑美元汇率触及三十年来的最低水平，令交易员对官方干预的风险感到紧张。</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Apr 2024 00:23:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/yen-its-weakest-decades-boj-meets-2024-04-26/</guid></item><item><title>路透调查显示全球经济今年剩余时间将保持增长</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/global-economy-set-stay-roll-rest-year-2024-04-26/</link><description>路透社对经济学家的一项调查显示，全球经济可能会在今年剩余时间乃至 2025 年保持强劲势头，打破此前对经济放缓的预期。经济学家表示，增长强于预期的可能性大于疲软。</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Apr 2024 00:22:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/global-economy-set-stay-roll-rest-year-2024-04-26/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：日本央行成为焦点，美国科技股提供支持</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-04-25/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 21:47:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-04-25/</guid></item><item><title>北约称，如果俄罗斯寻求与西方建立良好关系，中国必须停止援助俄罗斯</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-must-stop-aiding-russia-if-it-seeks-good-relations-with-west-nato-says-2024-04-25/</link><description>北约秘书长延斯·斯托尔滕贝格周四表示，如果中国想与西方保持良好关系，就必须停止支持俄罗斯在乌克兰的战争，并以异常严厉的措辞警告北京，不能两者兼得。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 18:36:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-must-stop-aiding-russia-if-it-seeks-good-relations-with-west-nato-says-2024-04-25/</guid></item><item><title>由于价格高企，全球葡萄酒需求跌至27年来的最低点</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/global-wine-demand-drops-27-year-low-high-prices-hit-2024-04-25/</link><description>国际葡萄与葡萄酒组织 (OIV) 周四表示，由于通货膨胀导致价格创历史新高，导致本已面临消费能力下降的消费者望而却步，全球葡萄酒消费量去年跌至 1996 年以来的最低水平。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 18:03:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/global-wine-demand-drops-27-year-low-high-prices-hit-2024-04-25/</guid></item><item><title>该机构禁止中国电信运营商提供美国宽带服务</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/media-telecom/agency-bars-chinese-telecom-carriers-offering-us-broadband-services-2024-04-25/</link><description>美国联邦通信委员会周四表示，正在命令中国电信、中国联通和中国移动的美国子公司停止在美国的固定或移动宽带互联网业务。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 17:12:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/media-telecom/agency-bars-chinese-telecom-carriers-offering-us-broadband-services-2024-04-25/</guid></item><item><title>独家：消息人士称，如果法律选择失败，字节跳动更愿意在美国关闭 TikTok</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/bytedance-prefers-tiktok-shutdown-us-if-legal-options-fail-sources-say-2024-04-25/</link><description>四位消息人士称，如果 TikTok 的所有者字节跳动用尽所有法律选择来对抗禁止该平台进入美国应用商店的立法，那么这家中国公司宁愿关闭其亏损的应用程序，也不愿出售它。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 16:36:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/bytedance-prefers-tiktok-shutdown-us-if-legal-options-fail-sources-say-2024-04-25/</guid></item></channel></rss>